〈'''工作认真点'''〉（{{lang-en|"R U Professional"}}）是2009年美国[[独立摇滚|独立摇滚]]乐队{{lang|en|[[The_Mae_Shi|The Mae Shi]]}}的讽刺歌曲，创作灵感源自男演员[[克里斯蒂安·贝尔|克里斯蒂安·贝尔]]2008年7月在《[[魔鬼終結者：未來救贖|终结者2018]]》片场发脾气时脱口而出的话。贝尔当时正与女演员[[布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德|布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德]]对戏，但因[[摄影指导|摄影指导]][[夏恩·赫尔博特|夏恩·赫尔博特]]意外走入视线感到很生气并出言斥责。2009年2月2日，事情经过的录音在{{lang|en|[[TMZ|TMZ]]}}网站公布。{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}就在当天谱写并录制歌曲，并于次日发布，声称歌曲是向贝尔致敬。乐队从录音中[[取樣_(音樂)|抽取]]贝尔的声音[[音乐恶搞|恶搞]]，还把他发脾气时脱口而出的“工作认真点”纳入其中。歌词涉及贝尔主演的多部电影，如《[[报童传奇|报童传奇]]》、《[[摇摆狂潮|摇摆狂潮]]》、《[[美色殺人狂|美色殺人狂]]》和《[[黑暗骑士|黑暗骑士]]》。

歌曲发布次日就上传到{{lang|en|[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}，且可通过{{lang|en|[[MediaFire|MediaFire]]}}下载。〈工作认真点〉获得普遍好评，评论称赞歌曲恶搞贝尔片场失态的效率十足。[[音乐电视网|音乐电视网]]将作品风格与[[新浪潮|新浪潮]]乐队{{lang|en|[[Devo|Devo]]}}相比。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》认为乐队以生动的[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行音乐]]向贝尔致敬，《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》赞扬歌曲创意十足，是很风趣的[[舞曲|舞曲]]。《[[多伦多太阳报|多伦多太阳报]]》认可歌词创意及运用演员失态音频的创作手段。《[[国家报|国家报]]》觉得《工作认真点》属电子流行歌曲，对贝尔此次事件在互联网上[[網絡爆紅短片|爆红]]贡献很大。《[[剂量_(杂志)|剂量]]》杂志将歌曲归入即兴[[电子放克音乐|电子放克音乐]]。《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》和{{lang|en|[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]}}都对乐队能在事件音频上网短短24小时内完成并发行歌曲颇感惊喜。《[[爱尔兰独立报|爱尔兰独立报]]》推测{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}是将此前创作的[[旋律|旋律]]改编后写进歌曲，所以才能这么快发布。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Christian_Bale_-_002.jpg|thumb]]（摄于2008年7月）]]

2008年7月，男演员[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]在[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]参与拍摄电影《[[魔鬼終結者：未來救贖|终结者2018]]》<ref name="bryant">{{cite news | last = Bryant | first = Adam | title = Christian Bale's Verbal Attack Draws Today's Attention | work = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170902133500/http://www.tvguide.com/news/christian-bale-today-1002384/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | url = https://www.tvguide.com/news/christian-bale-today-1002384/ | archivedate = 2017-09-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="afp">{{cite news | title = Holy expletive! Bale caught in on-set meltdown | agency = [[法新社|Agence France-Presse]] | date = 2009-02-03 | url = https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jaJT1WIl1cyzmCr1nW2LZxdGRZGw | accessdate = 2013-02-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224154712/https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jaJT1WIl1cyzmCr1nW2LZxdGRZGw | archivedate = 2013-02-24}}</ref>。就在他和女演员[[布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德|布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德]]对戏时，[[摄影指导|摄影指导]][[夏恩·赫尔博特|夏恩·赫尔博特]]（{{lang|en|Shane Hurlbut}}）意外走入视线，贝尔非常生气并大声斥责<ref name="bryant" /><ref name="foxnews">{{cite news | title = Christian Bale's F-Word-Laced Verbal Tirade Caught on Tape | work = [[福斯新聞頻道|Fox News]] | date = 2009-02-03 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.foxnews.com/story/christian-bales-f-word-laced-verbal-tirade-caught-on-tape | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180823105549/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2009/02/03/christian-bale-f-word-laced-verbal-tirade-caught-on-tape.html | archivedate = 2018-08-23}}</ref>。赫尔博特冷静地向贝尔道歉，事后继续参与摄制七小时<ref name="foxnews" /><ref name="msnbc">{{cite news | author = Access Hollywood | title = Christian Bale's profane tirade caught on tape: Actor berates director of photography who walked on set during filming | work = [[今天_(NBC)|Today.com]] | date = 2009-02-03 | publisher = NBC Universal | archivedate = 2017-09-18 | url = https://www.today.com/popculture/christian-bale-s-profane-tirade-caught-tape-wbna28984085 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170918143408/https://www.today.com/popculture/christian-bale-s-profane-tirade-caught-tape-wbna28984085}}</ref><ref name="bostonherald">{{cite news | last = Inside Track | title = Outburst reveals Christian Bale’s 'Dark' side | work = Boston Herald | date = 2009-02-04 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811111132/https://www.bostonherald.com/2009/02/04/outburst-reveals-christian-bales-dark-side/ | url = https://www.bostonherald.com/2009/02/04/outburst-reveals-christian-bales-dark-side/}}</ref>。

2009年2月2日，{{lang|en|[[TMZ|TMZ]]}}网站公布事情经过的录音<ref name="bryant" /><ref name="afp" />。音频全长四分钟，可以清楚地听到贝尔大声辱骂赫尔博特，声称如果再犯，剧组必须叫他卷铺盖走人，否则自己就退出<ref name="afp" /><ref name="foxnews" />。{{lang|en|TMZ}}网站曾于2008年7月报导事件经过<ref name="sweeney">{{cite news | last = Sweeney | first = Fionnuala | title = Bale's on set rant goes viral: TMZ's Mike Walters explains how they got the tape of Christian Bale's outburst on the set of 'Terminator Salvation.' | agency = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | date = 2009-02-05}}</ref>，《终结者2018》的制片公司高管将事件录音寄给保险公司，以防贝尔真的退出<ref name="foxnews" /><ref name="msnbc" />。

2009年2月6日，贝尔通过洛杉矶{{lang|en|[[KROQ-FM|KROQ-FM]]}}广播电台发布声明，承认行为失当，声称事后两人已通过交流彻底解决问题。贝尔还称，两人当天就在事情发生后继续共事好几个小时，此后又持续合作一个月。他还看过电影摄制完成后的早期版本，对赫尔博特的[[电影摄影|摄影]]功底十分满意。<ref name="bbcnews20090206">{{cite news | title = Actor Bale speaks out over rant: Film star Christian Bale has called a US radio station to apologise for a tirade which was leaked onto the internet, calling it 'inexcusable' | work = [[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]] | date = 2009-02-06 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7875756.stm | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191021040758/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7875756.stm | archivedate = 2019-10-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

