{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}发表声明解释创作〈工作认真点〉的灵感来源<ref name="jasongregory" /><ref name="kirby" />。乐队感觉贝尔当时很不理智，想为此写首歌<ref name="jasongregory" /><ref name="kirby" />。声明强调，歌曲意在向贝尔致敬，与乐队以往的传统作品无关<ref name="jasongregory">{{cite news | last = Gregory | first = Jason | title = Christian Bale Terminator Rant Turned Into A Tribute Song By The Mae Shi... | work = Gigwise | date = 2009-02-04 | url = https://www.gigwise.com/news/49156/Christian-Bale-Terminator-Rant-Turned-Into-A-Tribute-Song | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2017-09-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170911071204/http://www.gigwise.com/news/49156/Christian-Bale-Terminator-Rant-Turned-Into-A-Tribute-Song}}</ref><ref name="kirby">{{cite news | last = Kirby | first = Terry | title = Bale's furious rant becomes instant electro-dance hit | work = Evening Standard | agency = Associated Newspapers Limited | date = 2009-02-04 | url = https://www.standard.co.uk/news/bales-furious-rant-becomes-instant-electro-dance-hit-6880073.html | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2017-09-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170922002427/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/bales-furious-rant-becomes-instant-electro-dance-hit-6880073.html}}</ref>。

鼓手布拉德·布雷克（{{lang|en|Brad Breeck}}）在接受采访时称，乐队是在2009年2月2日晚决定针对事件创作歌曲<ref name="lore">{{cite news | last = Lore | first = Mark | title = Agit-pop: The road-worn Mae Shi take on Batman and Miley Cyrus | work = Chico News & Review | date = 2009-03-26 | url = https://www.newsreview.com/chico/agit-pop/content?oid=932633 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2017-11-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171120200418/https://www.newsreview.com/chico/agit-pop/content?oid=932633}}</ref>。各成员聆听贝尔失态的音频后在两小时内各自创作，把所有曲段综合后再从网上发布<ref name="lore" />。乐队另一名鼓手雅各布·库珀（{{lang|en|Jacob Cooper}}）向《[[亚利桑那每日星报|亚利桑那每日星报]]》（''{{lang|en|The Arizona Daily Star}}''）表示，他在歌曲创作和录制上投入的时间很少，对作品最终如此热门深感惊讶<ref name="kevinwsmith">{{cite news | first = Kevin W. | last = Smith | title = Mae Shi turns Bale's tirade into dance song | date = 2009-03-12 | newspaper = The Arizona Daily Star | page = 5 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811123348/https://tucson.com/entertainment/music/mae-shi-turns-bales-tirade-into-dance-song/article_c7a9bd92-11e1-5563-bfce-7ec6ea16e4d2.html | archivedate = 2020-08-11 | deadurl = no | url = https://tucson.com/entertainment/music/mae-shi-turns-bales-tirade-into-dance-song/article_c7a9bd92-11e1-5563-bfce-7ec6ea16e4d2.html}}</ref>。

〈工作认真点〉歌词涉及贝尔出演的多部电影，如《报童传奇》（''{{lang|en|Newsies}}''）<ref name="matheson">{{cite news | last = Matheson | first = Whitney | title = Hot trend o' the week: Christian Bale remixes | work = Pop Candy; [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archivedate = 2009-02-07 | accessdate = 2009-02-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090207075703/http://blogs.usatoday.com/popcandy/2009/02/hot-trend-o-the.html | url = http://blogs.usatoday.com/popcandy/2009/02/hot-trend-o-the.html?csp=34 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>、《摇摆狂潮》（''{{lang|en|Swing Kids}}''）<ref name="collins">{{cite news | last = Collins | first = Leah | title = The Best Thing I Ever Heard...This Week | journal = Dose | agency = Canwest Interactive | date = 2009-02-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120112195417/http://www.dose.ca/music/story.html?id=f627a31c-8075-4b4b-8a60-1fd6c26a403d | url = http://www.dose.ca/music/story.html?id=f627a31c-8075-4b4b-8a60-1fd6c26a403d | accessdate = 2012-01-12 | archivedate = 2012-01-12}}</ref>、《[[美色殺人狂|美色殺人狂]]》<ref name="reynolds">{{cite news | last = Reynolds | first = Simon | title = Bale tantrum becomes web phenomenon | agency = [[数码间谍|Digital Spy]] | date = 2009-02-04 | url = https://www.digitalspy.com/showbiz/a145639/bale-tantrum-becomes-web-phenomenon/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2015-10-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151001154623/http://www.digitalspy.com/celebrity/news/a145639/bale-tantrum-becomes-web-phenomenon.html}}</ref>，以及《[[黑暗骑士|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士]]》<ref name="unabronca" />。歌曲开头唱道：“他是黑暗骑士，工作很认真”<ref name="unabronca">{{cite news | last = OTR/PRESS News Agency | title = Una bronca de Christian Bale aprovechada como letra para una canción | newspaper = [[阿贝赛报|ABC newspaper]] | date = 2009-05-02 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.abc.es/estilo/gente/abci-bronca-christian-bale-aprovechada-como-letra-para-cancion-200902050300-912927276234_noticia.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170903205903/http://www.abc.es/20090205/gente-celebrities/bronca-christian-bale-aprovechada-200902050852.html | archivedate = 2017-09-03}}</ref>。乐队从事件录音中[[取樣_(音樂)|抽取]]贝尔的声音<ref name="collins" /><ref name="upi">{{cite news | title = Bale tirade becomes YouTube sensation | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archivedate = 2018-07-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180706022042/https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2009/02/03/Bale-tirade-becomes-YouTube-sensation/90221233694011/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | url = https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2009/02/03/Bale-tirade-becomes-YouTube-sensation/90221233694011/?ur3=1}}</ref>，合唱部分引述他发脾气时脱口而出的“工作认真点”：哇，老天爷/他工作真的好认真/但我觉得他有点失常<ref name="kirby" /><ref name="kaufman">{{cite news | last = Kaufman | first = Gil | title = You Can Now Dance To The Sound Of Christian Bale’s Fury | work = [[音樂電視網|MTV]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170911163857/http://www.mtv.com/news/2431517/you-can-now-dance-to-the-sound-of-christian-bales-fury/ | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/2431517/you-can-now-dance-to-the-sound-of-christian-bales-fury/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2017-09-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。其他歌词包括：“摇摆狂潮会带来暴力因子”<ref name="collins" />，“赶快退后，别让他看见/千万别想着要打架/报童今晚就会找上你/因为他们工作都很认真！”<ref name="matheson" />还有“可别注视他的双眼/他无法隐藏心中渴望/事态或许会一发不可收拾/你可能要遇上美国精神病人”<ref name="reynolds" />。

== 发布和反响 ==
