2009年2月3日，〈工作认真点〉通过{{lang|en|[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}和{{lang|en|[[MediaFire|MediaFire]]}}发布<ref>{{cite news | last = Sciretta | first = Peter | title = LOL: The Christian Bale Fun Continues | work = /film | date = 2009-02-03 | url = https://www.slashfilm.com/lol-the-christian-bale-fun-continues/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170907122654/http://www.slashfilm.com/lol-the-christian-bale-fun-continues/ | archivedate = 2017-09-07}}</ref>。乐队在{{lang|en|YouTube}}留下的视频描述写道：“{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}为祝贺克里斯蒂安·贝尔的工作和生活所创歌曲。贝尔在即将上映的电影终结者4《救赎》中扮演[[约翰·康纳|约翰·康纳]]，演出无疑会非常精彩，他的表演会赢得所有[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]的肯定，哪怕特效奖和动画奖也不例外”。<ref>{{cite news | title = Christian Bale Remixed | work = Pedestrian TV | date = 2009-02-03 | archivedate = 2018-08-29 | url = https://www.pedestrian.tv/music/christian-bale-remixed/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180829041957/https://www.pedestrian.tv/music/christian-bale-remixed/}}</ref>《[[独立报|独立报]]》称{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}将参加“粉丝反击战”（{{lang|en|The Fans Strike Back}}）音乐节，希望乐队届时表演《工作认真点》<ref>{{cite news | last = Harley | first =Kevin | title = Ten best gigs | newspaper = [[独立报|The Independent]] | page = 5; Section: The Information | date = 2009-05-02 | location = London}}</ref>。

媒体出版物将歌曲列入各种[[艺术类型|音乐流派]]。[[音乐电视网|音乐电视网]]将歌曲风格与{{lang|en|Devo}}乐队和[[新浪潮|新浪潮音乐]]对比<ref name="kaufman" />。《[[国家报|国家报]]》认为《工作认真点》是[[电子流行|电子流行]]歌曲，对贝尔此次事件在互联网上[[网络爆红短片|爆红]]贡献很大<ref>{{cite news | title = El hombre o la máquina | newspaper = [[国家报|El País]] | date = 2009-06-05 | url =  https://elpais.com/diario/2009/06/05/tentaciones/1244226173_850215.html | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313233453/http://elpais.com/diario/2009/06/05/tentaciones/1244226173_850215.html | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《剂量》杂志将歌曲归入即兴电子放克音乐，称赞乐队从事件音频中抽取贝尔语音的手法十分巧妙<ref name="collins" />。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》认为{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}以生动的[[流行_(音乐类型)|流行音乐]]向贝尔致敬<ref>{{cite news | last = Boucher | first = Geoff | title = Christian Bale, Robert Downey Jr., Kristen Bell and Skeletor, all in Everyday Hero headlines | work = Hero Complex; [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 2009-02-04 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2009/02/robert-downey-j.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170924182243/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/uncategorized/robert-downey-j/ | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2017-09-24 | archivedate = 2017-09-24}}</ref>。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》赞扬歌曲创意十足，是很风趣的[[舞曲|舞曲]]<ref name="matheson" />。《多伦多太阳报》（''{{lang|en|The Toronto Sun}}''）认可歌词创意及运用演员失态音频的创作手段，觉得歌曲融电子和流行音乐风格于一体，很适合当成舞曲<ref>{{cite news | last = Sterdan | first = Darryl | title = Down Stream; 3 Picks. 3 Clicks. 3 Cool Online Tracks | work = The Toronto Sun | page = E16 | date = 2009-02-15}}</ref>。《[[新音乐快递|新音乐快递]]》认为歌曲属电子摇滚乐，自始至终巧妙采用贝尔的声音，值得向读者推荐<ref>{{cite news | title = Christian Bale tirade – The Mae Shi record tribute song | journal = [[新音乐快递|New Musical Express]] | url = https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-mae-shi-2-1306716 | date = 2009-02-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116215739/https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-mae-shi-2-1306716 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archive-date = 2021-01-16 }}</ref>。《[[圣路易斯邮报|圣路易斯邮报]]》（''{{lang|en|St. Louis Post-Dispatch}}''）认为〈工作认真点〉属新浪潮音乐，其中采用事件录音中最耸人听闻的片段，最终效果非常有趣<ref name="mattfernandes">{{cite news | last = Fernandes | first = Matt | title = The Mae Shi, playing Gargoyle Sat., remix Christian Bale rant | newspaper = St. Louis Post-Dispatch | url = https://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/music/the-mae-shi-playing-gargoyle-sat-remix-christian-bale-rant/image_babc4bcf-cc34-5991-a49b-7ae4736d65c1.html | date = 2009-02-20 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811143054/https://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/music/the-mae-shi-playing-gargoyle-sat-remix-christian-bale-rant/image_babc4bcf-cc34-5991-a49b-7ae4736d65c1.html | archivedate = 2020-08-11}}</ref>。《亚利桑那每日星报》也觉得这首歌是流行舞曲<ref name="kevinwsmith" />。

多份评论着重强调{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}能用这么快的速度完成并发表歌曲。《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》认为〈工作认真点〉属于贝尔事件引发的[[网络迷因|网络迷因]]，虽然创作时间短，但娱乐效果和创意都很足<ref>{{cite news | last = Koski | first = Genevieve | title = "Fucking Distracting!!": Your meme of the week | work = [[影音俱乐部|The A.V. Club]] | date = 2009-02-06 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2019-11-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191121002111/https://film.avclub.com/fucking-distracting-your-meme-of-the-week-1798215693 | url = https://film.avclub.com/fucking-distracting-your-meme-of-the-week-1798215693}}</ref>。《[[爱尔兰独立报|爱尔兰独立报]]》同样对乐队创作速度感到惊喜，特别是在歌曲中有那么多段歌词讽刺贝尔失态言论的情况下<ref name="marsden" />。该报推测{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}是将此前创作的[[旋律|旋律]]改编后写进歌曲，所以才能这么快发布<ref name="marsden">{{cite news | last = Marsden | first = Rhodri | title = Christian Bale: All the rage on the web – The first clip appeared within minutes – and a week on, Christian Bale's fury is inspiring Oscar-worthy satire. Rhodri Marsden follows the links | work = [[爱尔兰独立报|Irish Independent]] | date = 2009-02-09 | url = https://www.independent.ie/business/technology/christian-bale-all-the-rage-on-the-web-26512530.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304141243/http://www.independent.ie/business/technology/christian-bale-all-the-rage-on-the-web-26512530.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-08-11}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]}}同样对《工作认真点》是在24小时内完成赞叹不已<ref name="richardson">{{cite news | last = Richardson | first = Mark | title = New Music: The Mae Shi ft. Christian Bale: "R U Professional" Stream | work = [[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] | date = 2009-02-03 | url = http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/download/148888-new-music-the-mae-shi-ft-christian-bale-r-u-professional-stream | accessdate = 2009-02-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090206080756/http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/download/148888-new-music-the-mae-shi-ft-christian-bale-r-u-professional-stream | archivedate = 2009-02-06}}</ref>。

许多评论认为{{lang|en|The Mae Shi}}向克里斯蒂安·贝尔及其作品致敬的方式相当独特。《[[波音波音|波音波音]]》认为这种致意十分有趣<ref>{{cite news | last = Bledsoe | first = Derek | title = BB Video: The Mae Shi are "Professionals" | work = [[波音波音|Boing Boing]] | date = 2009-03-17 | url = https://boingboing.net/2009/03/17/bb-video-the-mae-shi.html | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200731172935/https://boingboing.net/2009/03/17/bb-video-the-mae-shi.html | archivedate = 2020-07-31}}</ref>。{{lang|en|C7nema}}网站认为歌曲搞笑至极，是向贝尔的古怪行为“献礼”<ref>{{cite news | title = Salvar o futuro: a saga ‘Terminator’ – Parte IV | work = C7nema | date = 2009-06-03 | deadurl = no | url =  https://c7nema.net/artigos/item/35870-salvar-o-futuro-a-saga-terminator.html | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120727033218/http://www.c7nema.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1093&Itemid=33&limitstart=3 | archivedate = 2012-07-27}}</ref>。《名人咖啡馆》（{{lang|en|''The Celebrity Cafe''}}）认为〈工作认真点〉比[[盧西安·皮安|盧西安·皮安]]针对同一事件创作的歌曲〈[[贝尔要退出|贝尔要退出]]〉更出色<ref>{{cite news | last = Hunt | first = Kristin | title = A Funny Thing Happened . . . | work = The Celebrity Cafe | date = 2009-02-11 | archivedate = 2012-08-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120806191336/http://www.thecelebritycafe.com/features/24602.html | url = http://www.thecelebritycafe.com/features/24602.html | accessdate = 2012-08-06}}</ref>。[[哥谭派|芝加哥派]]（{{lang|en|Chicagoist}}）网站发文称，〈工作认真点〉是最优秀的克里斯蒂安·贝尔混录版歌曲<ref>{{cite news | title = Download: Batman Flips The F*#K Out | work = Chicagoist | date = 2009-02-04 | deadurl = no | url = https://chicagoist.com/2009/02/04/download_batman_flips_the_fk_out.php | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171108055015/http://chicagoist.com/2009/02/04/download_batman_flips_the_fk_out.php | archivedate = 2017-11-08}}</ref>。《[[新闻与评论|奇科新闻与评论]]》（''{{lang|en|Chico News & Review}}''）认为歌曲似乎是对贝尔失态行为的关心和赞誉<ref name="lore" />。

